  "title": "A Hunter Finds His Prey",
  "summary": "At the Imperial Embassy, bounty hunter Taggor Bren seeks out Vice-Director Joir, who is fielding a tedious briefing from his aides. Taggor reports that he has captured the man Joir wanted -- Normack Gastrov -- who is now waiting aboard his ship and carries knowledge the Empire will value. Retreating to a private office, Taggor presses Joir about the situation surrounding the Moff, and Joir, guarding sensitive information, reveals only that the Empire wants Lorn Rhys returned immediately. Satisfied, Taggor pledges his services, and the two part with a handshake, Joir promising to summon him when ready to interrogate Gastrov.",
